'''天主教科倫坡總教區''' （{{lang-la|Archidioecesis Columbensis in Taprobane}}）是[[斯里蘭卡|斯里蘭卡]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[總教區|總教區]]，也是該國唯一一個總教區。總教區下轄11個教區。

總教區管轄斯里蘭卡[[可倫坡區|可倫坡區]]、[[加姆珀哈區|加姆珀哈區]]和[[卡盧特勒區|卡盧特勒區]]，以及印度洋島國[[馬爾代夫|馬爾代夫]]，2006年時有700,000名教友、124個[[堂區|堂區]]和255名[[司鐸|司鐸]]。現任總主教為[[馬爾科姆·蘭吉特|馬爾科姆·蘭吉特]][[樞機|樞機]]<ref>{{cite web |title=PATABENDIGE DON Card. Albert Malcolm Ranjith |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/documentation/cardinali_biografie/cardinali_bio_patabendige-don_amr.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-07-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200715124641/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/documentation/cardinali_biografie/cardinali_bio_patabendige-don_amr.html |archivedate=2020-07-15 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>，輔理主教為{{link-en|薩姆帕塔瓦杜蓋·馬克斯韋爾·格倫維爾·西爾瓦|Sampathawaduge Maxwell Grenville Silva}}、{{link-de|賈亞科迪·阿拉特奇蓋·東·安多尼·賈亞科迪|Jayakody Aratchige Don Anton Jayakody}}和{{link-en|安多尼·蘭吉特·皮萊納亞加姆|Anton Ranjith Pillainayagam}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 28.11.2011 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2011/11/28/0713/01706.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2020-07-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200715102834/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2011/11/28/0713/01706.html |archivedate=2020-07-15 |language=it |date=2011-11-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Vatican20180404">{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 04.04.2018 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/04/04/180404b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-07-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200715120536/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/04/04/180404b.html |archivedate=2020-07-15 |language=en |date=2018-04-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 13.07.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/07/13/200713a.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-07-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200715084755/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/07/13/200713a.html |archivedate=2020-07-15 |language=en |date=2020-07-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休總主教為{{link-en|奧思華·戈米斯|Oswald Gomis|奧思華·多默·高爾孟·戈米斯}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 16.06.2009 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2009/06/16/0407/00945.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2020-07-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200715122732/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2009/06/16/0407/00945.html |archivedate=2020-07-15 |language=it |date=2009-06-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休輔理主教為{{link-de|雲先·佩里斯|Vincent Peiris|雲先·瑪略·若瑟·佩里斯}}<ref name="Vatican20180404" />。

[[天主教果亞暨達曼總教區|果亞教區]]於1533年成立，斯里蘭卡歸其管轄，後轉歸[[天主教科欽教區|科欽教區]]，至1834年設'''錫蘭宗座代牧區'''，1849年易名'''科倫坡宗座代牧區'''。錫蘭於1887年行聖統制，升為總教區。

